arStrings.szText: The Scholar and I have traced the steps of a non-believer named Batzorig, sought by the Hand of Zakarum, to a cellar where he attempted to hide from persecution. In reenacting his defense, he has possessed Nurbolat. I must now defend myself against him.

The Scholar and I have traced the steps of a non-believer named Batzorig, sought by the Hand of Zakarum, to a cellar where he attempted to hide from persecution. In reenacting his defense, he possessed Nurbolat. I had to defend myself against him, until he had an epiphany. I should speak with him.
